Content-Type: application/json

{
  "mode": "auto",
  "lighting": { "enabled": true, "schedule": { "on": "06:00", "off": "18:00" } },
  "fan": { "enabled": true, "temperature": { "on": 28, "off": 24 } },
  "feeder": { "enabled": true, "weight": { "min": 5, "max": 20 } },
  "waterPump": { "enabled": true }
}

### Consultar configuração
GET http://localhost:3000/api/config

### Registrar ação manual
POST http://localhost:3000/api/actions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "system": "water",
  "action": "activate",
  "quantity": 1
}

### Listar ações
GET http://localhost:3000/api/actions?system=water&limit=5

### Cadastrar dispositivo
POST http://localhost:3000/api/devices
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Ventoinha 1",
  "type": "fan",
  "status": "off"
}

### Listar dispositivos
GET http://localhost:3000/api/devices

### Consultar dispositivo por ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/devices/1

### Atualizar dispositivo
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/devices/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Ventoinha 1",
  "type": "fan",
  "status": "on"
}

### Remover dispositivo
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/devices/1
